      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ We Ludwig IV by God's grace Grand Duke of Hesse and by Rhine &amp;c have awarded the Commander's Cross 1st class with crown of Our Order of Merit of Philip the Magnanimous to the Government Botanist fo...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">87.06.21</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Ludwig IV, Grand Duke of Hesse</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M200a.57, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is a printed certificate.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">Wir Ludwig IV</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">von Gottes Gnaden</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">Grossherzog von Hessen</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">und bei Rhein pp.</seg>
               </seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">praemissis praemittendis [= &amp;c]</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">haben dem</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Regierungs-Botaniker für die Colonie Victoria in Australien</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">Dr. med: Ferdinand von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">Das Comthurkreuz 1ter Classe mit der Krone</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">
                  <seg style="">Unseres Verdienstordens Philipps des Grossmüthigen verliehen. Urkundlich Unserer Eigenhändigen Unterschrift und beigedrückten Grossherzoglichen Siegels</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>London, am 21ten Juni 1887.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ludwig</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">In Erledigung der Ordenskanzler Stelle:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Wernher</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>We Ludwig IV by God's grace Grand Duke of Hesse and by Rhine &amp;c have awarded the Commander's Cross 1st class with crown of Our Order of Merit of Philip the Magnanimous to the Government Botanist for the Colony of Victoria in Australia Dr. med. Ferdinand von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Attested by our signature in our own hand and impressed grandducal seal.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">London, 21 June 1887</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ludwig</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">In discharge of the Chancellor of the Order's authority:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wernher</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
